products.title: Choices Chenille Chic Pearl Roller Blind
products.metadescription: With plushness in abundance and plenty of style, this choices chenille chic pearl roller blind isn't just yet another off-white offering, no.  It's full of texture like nothing before it, with a cool colourway that delivers modernity into your home as well as cosy vibes.
